OL,3,COfficer in critical condition after
OL,4,Ccrash involving police car
OL,6,FA crash involving a police car has
OL,7,Fleft an officer with life-threatening
OL,8,Finjuries.
OL,10,FNorthumbria Police said its officer is
OL,11,Fin a critical condition in hospital
OL,12,Ffollowing the collision in the
OL,13,FCramlington area on Monday (8 June)
OL,14,Fnight which has closed the A189 Spine
OL,15,FRoad for more than 13 hours.
OL,17,FThe force received a report of a two-
OL,18,Fvehicle collision on the southbound
OL,19,Fcarriageway, near to Moor Farm
OL,20,FRoundabout, shortly after 11:10pm.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
