PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1781266277
OL,3,COfficer in critical condition after
OL,4,Ccrash involving police car
OL,6,FIt is understood that a silver Land
OL,7,FRover Freelander collided with a white
OL,8,FFord Explorer. The Ford left the road
OL,9,Fand the occupants of the Land Rover
OL,10,Ffled the area on foot before police
OL,11,Farrived, the force said.
OL,13,FEmergency services attended where no
OL,14,Fserious injuries were reported.
OL,16,FA black Mercedes CLC then collided
OL,17,Fwith a marked Northumbria Police car
OL,18,Fthat was also on the southbound
OL,19,Fcarriageway - leaving an officer
OL,20,Fseriously injured.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
