CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1781266277
OL,3,COfficer in critical condition after
OL,4,Ccrash involving police car
OL,6,FThe officer was taken to hospital and
OL,7,Fremains there in a critical condition.
OL,9,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FThe driver of the Mercedes ` a 73-year-
OL,15,Fold man ` was arrested on suspicion of
OL,16,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,17,Fdriving and he remains in police
OL,18,Fcustody at this time.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
