OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1781266277
OL,3,COfficer in critical condition after
OL,4,Ccrash involving police car
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Helena
OL,7,FBarron, of Northumbria Police, said:
OL,8,F"Our thoughts are very much with the
OL,9,Fofficer, their loved ones and all
OL,10,Fthose impacted by what has happened.
OL,11,FWe will continue to support their
OL,12,Ffamily and colleagues at this
OL,13,Fdifficult time."
OL,15,FA North East Ambulance Service
OL,16,Fspokesperson said: "We were called to
OL,17,Fa road traffic incident on the A189
OL,18,FSpine Road in Cramlington shortly
OL,19,Fbefore midnight on Monday 8 June.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
