PN,42505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1781266277
OL,3,COfficer in critical condition after
OL,4,Ccrash involving police car
OL,6,F"We dispatched two ambulance crews,
OL,7,Fone duty officer and were supported by
OL,8,Four colleagues at Great North Air
OL,9,FAmbulance Service. Two patients were
OL,10,Ftaken to hospital by road for further
OL,11,Ftreatment."
OL,13,FOfficers from the Force's Serious
OL,14,FCollision Investigation Unit are
OL,15,Fappealing for any witnesses, anyone
OL,16,Fwho was travelling in the area and who
OL,17,Fmight have dashcam footage to get in
OL,18,Ftouch.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
