OL,3,COfficer in critical condition after
OL,4,Ccrash involving police car
OL,6,FAnyone with information should call
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police on 101 and quote
OL,8,Freference number NP-20260608-1198.
OL,10,FThe road remains closed.
